from arromdee ken arromdee subject re american jewish congres open letter to clinton in article casper casper write i must say i wa appal by the american jewish council open letter america be not the world policeman we can not and should not take it upon ourself to solve the problem of the entire world america young man and woman should not be send to yugoslavium period if person feel strongly enough let them go a individual to fight alongside the butcher of their choice we have a volunteer army the argument you give only apply if we have a draft huh sorry i misread ymy remark about young man and woman though i be now unsure what that sentence do mean furthermore person do not become butcher by be ethnic cleanse or do you automatically call them butcher because they be muslim i be disappoint in ymy logic especially come from a stalwart of you imply that anyone who want to send troop to bosnium want to do so to help the butcher of their choice since the primary target of help be muslim victim of ethnic cleanse you imply that such muslim victim be butcher person become butcher by butcher there have be atrocity on all side thi imply both side be equal true it may sometime be difficult or impossible to determine which side be the victim but that do not mean that victim do not exist would you in wwius have say that there be atrocity on the side of both the jew and the german these person have be butcher each other for century when one side win and get what it want it will stop ye but both side want different thing the muslim chiefly want to not be ethnic cleanse the serbian want to ethnic cleanse the muslim it be indeed true that each side will stop when it get what it want but the thing that the two side want be not equivalent quite an impressive leap of reason to assume that i be so racist a to call someone a butcher because they be muslim in fact i think on the contrary the medium fixation on thi war a oppose to the dozen upon dozen of civil war which have be fight in